headline: BD Gets FDA 510(k) Approval for EnCor EnCompass Breast Biopsy System
summary: BDX wins FDA 510(k) clearance for the EnCor EnCompass breast biopsy system, set for an early 2026 launch to boost flexibility and patient care.
